snippet.title: Power Chord - Official Gameplay Trailer | Summer of Gaming 2022
snippet.description:
Take a look at gameplay in this trailer for Power Chord, an upcoming rock'n roguelite deck-building game coming to PC via Steam in Q3 2022. A demo for the game will be available during Steam Next Fest starting on June 13, 2022.

#GameTrailers
